Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.35,0:02:11.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}[...道别之日.]
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.81,0:02:15.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小鸠
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.15,0:02:18.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么边睡边笑的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.73,0:02:22.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶?我笑了吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.31,0:02:25.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一脸无比幸福的微笑
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.62,0:02:27.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是做了很美的梦吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.29,0:02:29.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是 是的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.20,0:02:31.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很久以前...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.61,0:02:34.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊咧?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.53,0:02:37.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.57,0:02:38.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.71,0:02:46.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然是非常幸福的梦可是...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.79,0:02:51.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是关于你想去的地方的梦吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.37,0:03:30.24,XXX,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}(闭园通知  擅自作此决定非常抱歉，本保育园已经决定闭园。在此深表歉意。另，如有需要联络之事宜，请联系园长冲浦清花。     艾草保育园  冲浦清花)
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.60,0:03:56.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.90,0:03:59.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好 小鸠
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.87,0:04:02.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天要收拾哪里呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.04,0:04:08.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我先走了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.93,0:04:10.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.46,0:04:19.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很辛苦吧 有这么多被子
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.36,0:04:21.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没关系 我会一直努力的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.39,0:04:26.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 旧的不去新的不来嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.63,0:04:30.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,旧的不去 吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.82,0:04:38.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,捆好的东西就搬到玄关去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.91,0:04:39.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.13,0:04:49.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把这里弄完了就去喝茶吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.46,0:04:50.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.80,0:04:54.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,藤本君不在还真是累人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.25,0:04:59.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,忙着工作嘛 藤本先生他
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.14,0:05:05.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢惠顾
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.34,0:05:15.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里的工作 不用勉强加太多哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.55,0:05:17.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 请让我做
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.00,0:05:20.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经没有拼命挣钱的必要了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.71,0:05:22.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果要炒我就直说
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.10,0:05:25.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是的 不是那样的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.49,0:05:29.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 没法说你
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.61,0:05:35.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.44,0:05:40.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,决定关闭保育园
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.41,0:05:41.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.13,0:05:45.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过啊 有一点希望你能明白
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.86,0:05:49.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在我觉得这样就挺好的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.90,0:05:53.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我没有后悔
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.29,0:05:57.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是因为冲浦让我这样做才做的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.35,0:06:00.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最后作出这个决定的是我自己
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.12,0:06:02.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是这么想的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.21,0:06:06.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.83,0:06:24.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么事
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.10,0:06:28.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个 能请你去保育园一趟吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.10,0:06:32.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那里...那个...还有藤本先生的行李
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.69,0:06:33.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.23,0:06:37.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全扔了都没关系
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.47,0:06:38.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.32,0:06:39.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我很忙 去不了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.66,0:07:05.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是藤本
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.47,0:07:08.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思 我得晚到大概一小时
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.18,0:07:47.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.91,0:07:56.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,藤本先生?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.52,0:08:39.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要命啦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.85,0:08:53.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊咧?听说你今天会晚来啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.14,0:08:55.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,事办完就来了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.56,0:09:15.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哼 为什么这么一副郁闷的表情啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.88,0:09:19.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弄得我都郁闷得发急啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.25,0:09:22.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.09,0:09:28.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在想什么呢 你想做什么
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.51,0:09:32.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.96,0:09:34.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.50,0:09:35.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.62,0:09:40.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里很痛
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.39,0:09:43.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾草保育园要闭园了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.06,0:09:47.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对于清花老师是件好事
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.06,0:09:49.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.29,0:09:53.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是藤本啊?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.59,0:09:56.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.05,0:09:59.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,藤本先生吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.51,0:10:01.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么啊 你那反应
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.52,0:10:05.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你自己没发觉吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.78,0:10:06.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.70,0:10:11.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呀咧呀咧 真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.07,0:10:34.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,清和君
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.28,0:10:36.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.93,0:10:38.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天也要去打工吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.50,0:10:39.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.51,0:10:43.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是 今天是保育园房子拆除的日子...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.15,0:10:43.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我走了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.15,0:10:49.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天休息一天也没什么的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.68,0:10:51.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.95,0:10:56.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,邻居也出门了 我也出门一趟
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.16,0:10:57.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要出门吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.80,0:11:00.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 晚上回来
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.27,0:11:03.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要老是那副臭脸
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.88,0:11:04.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.96,0:11:08.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 你也抓紧点 要迟到了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.34,0:11:09.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 是
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.86,0:11:11.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玻璃全部拆掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.36,0:11:12.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再倒 再倒...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.17,0:11:14.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 STOP
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.33,0:11:17.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幸苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.26,0:11:20.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老师 行李都收拾好了?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.88,0:11:23.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昨天一天已经搬出去了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.79,0:11:27.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那 就抓紧开始干活吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.50,0:11:29.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个眼神凶巴巴的家伙呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.00,0:11:31.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有工作在身
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.45,0:11:34.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么嘛 真不讨人喜欢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.41,0:11:37.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明一直在这里受人照顾 真是无情呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.69,0:11:39.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才不是无情
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.20,0:11:44.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,藤本先生 真的很忙
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.28,0:11:51.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊啊 不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.93,0:11:56.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是受冲浦先生所托 让我仔细周到点
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.88,0:11:59.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他说最近来不了了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.22,0:12:01.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是 我已经听说了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.13,0:12:04.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像上面有很多事情要处理
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.15,0:12:08.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像我们这样的小喽啰当然不知道内情
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.87,0:12:11.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这么说来 冲浦先生...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.47,0:12:14.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用担心 一定会顺利解决的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.59,0:12:16.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为是冲浦先生嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.45,0:12:17.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.86,0:12:19.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,清花老师
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.93,0:12:21.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小鸠
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.34,0:12:22.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.80,0:12:23.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.24,0:12:26.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个...因为今天就要说再见了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.18,0:12:28.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以来看看
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.54,0:12:31.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经和妈妈说好了才来的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.45,0:12:32.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.60,0:12:33.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你们
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.45,0:12:36.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,头儿 可以开始了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.74,0:12:40.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老师 可以开始了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.38,0:12:56.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜托了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.93,0:13:00.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了 很危险大家都退得远一点吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.03,0:13:02.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是~
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.92,0:13:04.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 开始吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.24,0:13:34.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜拜
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.89,0:13:45.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我再说一遍
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.88,0:13:48.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这事没什么可商量的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.87,0:13:53.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,断了这个念头吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.06,0:13:58.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 玄琥大人太狡猾了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.72,0:14:00.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然不等我就吃点心了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.38,0:14:02.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我开动了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.98,0:14:05.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瑞祥 安静点
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.64,0:14:06.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.61,0:14:08.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊?诶?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.98,0:14:14.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶?居然想抓住兔子先生?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.23,0:14:16.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.31,0:14:19.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把兔子先生作为人质和那家伙交涉
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.74,0:14:24.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你真的觉得神会和你做那种交易吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.29,0:14:25.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总比什么都不做强啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.87,0:14:29.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把我们现在这状态都算在一起的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.34,0:14:31.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是说改就能改的契约
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.63,0:14:33.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,银生说的没错
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.63,0:14:36.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不像你说的话那么没分寸
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.69,0:14:41.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,事情的轻重而已
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.71,0:14:43.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,事情完了想它怎样它就怎样
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.29,0:14:45.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给我适可而止吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.27,0:14:48.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你那时候没有学到一点教训吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.59,0:14:49.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手 两位
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.35,0:14:53.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还没吃够苦头吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.30,0:14:57.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道会伤害到谁的话 我来告诉你吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.30,0:15:02.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.16,0:15:03.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.60,0:15:07.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘛 算了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.17,0:15:12.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,神想要你学习的 也许就是等待
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.68,0:15:16.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哼 那确实是我不擅长的领域
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.78,0:15:17.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.01,0:15:21.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道了啊 我什么都不会做的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.59,0:16:06.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我叫五百祗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.87,0:16:10.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今后会和你在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.09,0:16:26.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老师
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.17,0:16:30.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,收拾完了就不能再进去了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.48,0:16:32.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 辛苦你了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.27,0:16:36.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老师你们保重 再见
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.27,0:16:48.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本来还以为这里挺大的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.61,0:16:50.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样子看上去...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.92,0:16:52.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呐
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.36,0:17:04.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小鸠 有件事想要拜托你 可以吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.12,0:17:07.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶?好的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.96,0:17:11.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请你帮帮藤本君吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.79,0:17:12.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.96,0:17:18.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾草保育院可能一直都在束缚着藤本君
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.13,0:17:20.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是这样想的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.03,0:17:24.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,束缚着是指...什么呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.08,0:17:30.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让藤本君作为努力的藤本君生活着
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.34,0:17:36.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也一直依赖着藤本君
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.40,0:17:41.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是能早点察觉到就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.25,0:17:47.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你 藤本君
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.98,0:17:51.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,清和老师
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.47,0:17:52.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弹风琴给我们听
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.03,0:18:09.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了自己 去做自己喜欢的事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.74,0:18:11.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我早就该这样对他说的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.31,0:18:15.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪有 藤本先生是真的...很努力地...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.42,0:18:19.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 正因为这样才更是如此
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.73,0:18:23.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是因为藤本君太过努力了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.63,0:18:26.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以啊 小鸠
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.34,0:18:31.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,藤本君就拜托你了 陪在他身边吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.82,0:18:33.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,清花老师才是...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.26,0:18:39.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那不是我的角色了 已经不是了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.61,0:18:50.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小鸠
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.18,0:18:52.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小鸠
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.51,0:18:54.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 我回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.94,0:18:56.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小鸠 不好了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.66,0:18:58.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.28,0:19:08.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,堂元 你...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.60,0:19:13.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可是遵守约定没有联系保育园的人哦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.88,0:19:15.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只不过对管理人小姐说了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.93,0:19:16.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,切
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.02,0:19:21.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉啊小鸠 他说不想让你们担心
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.51,0:19:23.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他也是不愿麻烦你们...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.02,0:19:49.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个...手...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.90,0:19:57.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太 太好了呢 只是一点轻伤
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.98,0:20:01.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要太勉强了哦 大家都会担心你的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.71,0:20:08.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有一只手不能用的话很不方便吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.61,0:20:11.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什么事我能帮忙的话尽管告诉我
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.75,0:20:21.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一开始在艾草保育园那遇到你的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.38,0:20:24.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我应该说过吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.43,0:20:29.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要抱有什么同情和好奇心
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.33,0:20:36.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果你觉得我很可怜的话 请你省省吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.06,0:20:37.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是这样子的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.88,0:20:39.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很烦人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.06,0:20:47.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是的...藤本先...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.04,0:20:59.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是的...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.53,0:21:31.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是...给我的吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.58,0:21:38.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.83,0:21:42.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是让你在下次满月之前收集好金平糖啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.93,0:21:43.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,否则的话...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.43,0:21:47.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就会按照契约决定你的未来了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.01,0:21:51.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兔子先生啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.18,0:21:56.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要怎么样才能延长那个期限啊?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.71,0:22:02.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下来会怎么样?你认为该怎么做?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.39,0:22:04.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道呢 要看那家伙自己了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.25,0:22:08.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,应该是确实地感受到自己的责任了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.81,0:22:10.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有那场战斗的话
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.90,0:22:12.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那孩子就...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.56,0:22:19.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不会被殃及 出那种事了...吗
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.65,0:22:22.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要是我能做到的话什么都会去做
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.33,0:22:25.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以 在四季再轮回一次以前...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.75,0:22:27.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 一季也好
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.47,0:22:30.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,求求你了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.30,0:22:42.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是不行啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.34,0:22:43.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂

Dialogue: 0,0:24:25.40,0:24:29.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an3}[...小鸠的愿望.]

Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.21,0:23:11.81,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}{\an8}なくしたものと あつめたものの狭間に
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.21,0:23:11.81,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}所失与所得的缝隙中
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.42,0:23:20.26,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}{\an8}あなたの笑顔　落ちていたの
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.42,0:23:20.26,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}遗落着你的笑颜
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.65,0:23:26.04,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}{\an8}届きそうで　届かない
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.65,0:23:26.04,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}仿佛伸手可及却又遥不可及
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.23,0:23:31.99,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}{\an8}飛んでゆけるわけじゃないし
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.23,0:23:31.99,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}飞又飞不起来
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.15,0:23:38.19,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}{\an8}笑わせてあげたいだけなのに
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.15,0:23:38.19,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}我只是想让你有更多笑容
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.43,0:23:43.55,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}{\an8}役立たずのこの翼
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.43,0:23:43.55,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}这没用的双翼
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.88,0:23:49.32,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}{\an8}何のためにあるのだろう
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.88,0:23:49.32,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}到底为什么存在呢
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.09,0:23:55.73,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}{\an8}あなたの傍で笑うよ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.09,0:23:55.73,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}我会在你身边微笑
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.01,0:24:00.57,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}{\an8}私に出来ること
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.01,0:24:00.57,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}这是我能做到的事
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.06,0:24:07.41,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}{\an8}暖めるだけでもいいのかな
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.06,0:24:07.41,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}哪怕给你一丝为暖也好
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.66,0:24:12.03,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}{\an8}せめて包みたい
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.66,0:24:12.03,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}至少想包容着你
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.49,0:24:19.35,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}{\an8}気付くの　そのための翼と
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.49,0:24:19.35,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}终于发觉 双翼是为此存在
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.55,0:24:27.89,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}{\an8}今こそわたし　笑うよ
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.55,0:24:27.89,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}所以我现在 在微笑
